#. type: Plain text
#: origin/systemd.txt:85
msgid ""
"systemd can be installed alongside SysVinit and will start any init scripts "
"which do not have systemd equivalent unit files yet. It can also be "
"installed to fully replace SysVinit. In this guide systemd will first be "
"installed alongside SysVinit, then it can be tested, while optionally "
"booting into SysVinit or systemd. When satisfied that everything works well "
"in systemd, SysVinit can be completely replaced by systemd, and the init "
"scripts can be removed."
msgstr ""

